OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FA man has promised to bring his
OL,7,Fparents home to Orpington after they
OL,8,Fdied in an Air India Crash to London
OL,9,FGatwick.
OL,11,FAshok Patel, 74, and Shobhana Patel,
OL,12,F71, have lived in Greater London since
OL,13,Fthe 80s. Ashok was a financial
OL,14,Fadvisor, while Shobahana a
OL,15,Fmicrobiologist.
OL,17,FThe pair travelled to India for a
OL,18,Freligious trip known as a Yatra which
OL,19,Fhelps people find peace when they
OL,20,Feventually pass away.
