OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FUnfortunately, just days later, they
OL,7,Fwere among 53 British nationals that
OL,8,Fdied in a fatal plane crash in
OL,9,FAhmedabad, West India just minutes
OL,10,Fafter take off.
OL,12,FIt is still uncertain when the pair
OL,13,Fwill be returned to London though the
OL,14,Fprocess to identify them was quick.
OL,16,FTheir son, Miten, went to India and
OL,17,Fdescribes the process as a "miracle".
