OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FHe added "it's a result of meticulous
OL,7,Fand efficient planning" which meant he
OL,8,Fhad to put his grief to the side to
OL,9,Ffocus on fulfilling his parents'
OL,10,Fwishes.
OL,12,F"I haven't come to terms with it. My
OL,13,Fmain priority was the promise I made
OL,14,Fmy parents to bring them home," he
OL,15,Fsays.
OL,17,FHe is one of dozens of British family
OL,18,Fmembers who have flown to Ahmedabad to
OL,19,Fidentify and bring their loved ones
OL,20,Fback.
