OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,F"It is not an easy process when there
OL,7,Fare so many people that have gone
OL,8,Fthrough this tragedy," he tells ITV
OL,9,FNews London.
OL,11,FDespite how difficult the last seven
OL,12,Fdays have been, Miten praises his
OL,13,Ffamily and the wider community for all
OL,14,Ftheir kindness and support in the
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,17,FIt all began, when Miten received a
OL,18,Fphone call from his father's friend
OL,19,Fwho was in India.
OL,21,F"I couldn't believe it," he says.
