OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,F"I was with him on Father's Day, I
OL,7,Fheld him...that's the first time in
OL,8,Fthis whole ordeal I cried because I
OL,9,Ffelt like I was actually hugging my
OL,10,Fdad."
OL,12,FMiten contacted insurance companies,
OL,13,Fcollected dental records and DNA
OL,14,Fsamples to take to India in order to
OL,15,Fsupport the identification process.
