OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FHe says it was fate that his mother
OL,7,Fwas identified just four hours after
OL,8,Fhis father was, and added: "It felt
OL,9,Flike my mum was saying to my dad, stay
OL,10,Fwhere you are, you're not going alone,
OL,11,FI'm coming with you."
OL,13,FIn India, he was shown items that
OL,14,Fbelonged to his parents that were
OL,15,Ffound among the wreckage, from the
OL,16,Flabel of his father's beloved Stafford
OL,17,Fshirt to his mother swan-pendant
OL,18,Fnecklace that Miten's young daughter
OL,19,FAmira will now inherit.
