OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,F"My mum used to say one day you will
OL,7,Fhave that. It just feels like she's
OL,8,Fleft that necklace for her," he says.
OL,10,FOnce his parents are back in the UK,
OL,11,FMiten aims to hold a funeral service
OL,12,Ffor them both together.
OL,14,F"They have made it this far together
OL,15,Fso I would like to send them off
OL,16,Ftogether," he says.
