OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FWhile Miten's dad Ashok was born in
OL,7,FIndia and his family have ethnic roots
OL,8,Fto the country, India was an 'unknown
OL,9,Fcountry' for Miten who grew up in the
OL,10,FUK.
OL,12,F"I'm just glad I was able to fulfil my
OL,13,Fpromise that I made to my parents and
OL,14,Fmy family that I will make sure that
OL,15,Fthey come home because the UK is their
OL,16,Fhome."
OL,18,F"They've been here for over 40 years."
