OL,3,CA son speaks of his determination
OL,4,Cafter losing his parents in tragedy
OL,6,FMiten says his parents finally being
OL,7,Fcremated will start off a more
OL,8,Fpersonal mourning process for him that
OL,9,Fhe has been delaying.
OL,11,F"Once I get them home and we give them
OL,12,Fa good send off then I'll grieve in my
OL,13,Fown time, but at the moment I've just
OL,14,Fgot to stay strong for them," he says.
